<MELItem itemNbr="32-09-01" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-32-09-01.1.2-32-09-01">
<Title>Air/Ground Sensors</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="8" nbrRequired="4" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One tilt sensor on each main landing gear and one strut compression sensor on each main landing gear may be inoperative.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>On the LNDG GEAR INDN AND STRNG maintenance page, verify that no more than one tilt sensor and one strut compression sensor are inoperative on each main landing gear (AMM DDG 32-09-01).</Para>
<Note>
<Para>An inoperative TILT or STRT sensor will have an “x” in the status field.  </Para>
</Note>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
